title: Mantu Cager (Manistutu Camping Ground)
address: Unnamed Road, Manistutu, Kec. Melaya, Kabupaten Jembrana, Bali 82252
note_from_owner:
Manistutu Camping Ground di Jembrana adalah destinasi camping yang menawarkan pengalaman alam yang menakjubkan. Terletak di kawasan yang dikelilingi oleh pepohonan hijau dan pemandangan alam yang indah, tempat ini sangat cocok untuk pecinta alam dan petualangan.
Fasilitas
- Area Camping: Tersedia area luas untuk mendirikan tenda dengan akses mudah ke sumber air.
- Kamar Mandi dan Toilet:Fasilitas sanitasi yang bersih dan terawat.
- Tempat Berkumpul: Area untuk berkumpul dan bersosialisasi, dilengkapi dengan tempat duduk.
- Api Unggun: Tersedia area untuk membuat api unggun, ideal untuk berkumpul di malam hari.
Suasana
Suasana di Manistutu Camping Ground sangat tenang dan damai, jauh dari kebisingan kota. Suara alam, seperti kicauan burung

title: Muntig Kumpi ayu
address: Manistutu, Negara, Jembrana Regency, Bali 82252
note_from_owner:
This is special recreational place between the mountains, palm trees and jungle. Fresh air, beautiful ladscapes.
In this amazing beautiful place You can take a easy hike to secret temple in jungle woods, explore Balenese nature and culture.
In evening we are inviting You to take a peaceful rest on the hill, with beatifull landscape.
We serve fresh indonesian food.
Also there You will find amenities like shower and toilet.

If You wish we can offer extreem ride in Jungle with bugee (jeep).

description.description_one: Overlooking Waduk Palasari reservoir, this tropical resort is 2.6 km from Gereja Palasari palace and 26 km from Taman Nasional Bali Barat, Bali's only national park.
description.description_two: With vaulted ceilings and sitting areas, the contemporary rooms offer Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minibars, as well as coffeemakers and balconies with garden or water views. There are also villas with private pools. Room service is available.
description.description_three: Breakfast is offered. There's a genteel restaurant, a coffee shop, an outdoor pool and a spa, as well as bike rentals. Activities such as fishing, village and national park tours can be arranged.

description_arr: Overlooking Waduk Palasari reservoir, this tropical resort is 2.6 km from Gereja Palasari palace and 26 km from Taman Nasional Bali Barat, Bali's only national park.

With vaulted ceilings and sitting areas, the contemporary rooms offer Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minibars, as well as coffeemakers and balconies with garden or water views. There are also villas with private pools. Room service is available.
Breakfast is offered. There's a genteel restaurant, a coffee shop, an outdoor pool and a spa, as well as bike rentals. Activities such as fishing, village and national park tours can be arranged.
